videos.description: Michigan State shows off great ball movement to set Nick Ward up for a lay-in plus the foul.
videos.headline: Ward double pumps for and-1 layup

videos.description: Miles Bridges goes up for a layup but is blocked by Aaron Jordan, who wedges the ball between the rim and backboard.
videos.headline: Bridges has layup pinned between rim and backboard

videos.description: Michigan State's Jaren Jackson Jr. takes on contact in the lane then completes the and-1 slam with authority.
videos.headline: Jackson rocks the rim after being fouled

videos.description: Illinois head coach Brad Underwood gets very upset with his team early in the second half, he then unloaded his anger on them.
videos.headline: Underwood goes on screaming rampage during timeout

videos.description: Michigan State's Gavin Schilling takes over the paint with a powerful slam.
videos.headline: Schilling smashes down a one-handed flush

videos.description: Michigan State shows off its high-flying ability with dunks by Kenny Goins and Xavier Tillman.
videos.headline: Spartans hammer the rim on back-to-back possessions

videos.description: Michigan State's Miles Bridges gets an ovation during what may be his last game played in East Lansing.
videos.headline: Bridges emotional leaving court in potential final home game

videos.description: Tom Izzo and his three seniors shed tears as they walk off the court during senior night at Michigan State.
videos.headline: Izzo gets emotional saying goodbye to his three seniors

videos.description: Michigan State head coach Tom Izzo shares what Lourawls Nairn Jr. means to him, and what it means to clinch a share of the Big Ten title.
videos.headline: Izzo elated over storybook ending to senior night

videos.description: The balanced attack of the No. 2 Spartans is too much for the Fighting Illini, going on to win 81-61.
videos.headline: Michigan State cruises on senior night
